    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a YANG data model ([RFC6020], [RFC7950]) for
   segment routing ([RFC8402]) configuration and operation.  This YANG
   model is intended to be used on network elements to configure or
   operate segment routing.  This document defines also generic
   containers that SHOULD be reused by IGP protocol modules to support
   segment routing.</t>
    </abstract>
